      "description": "CL-CRI-1036 is a cluster of financially motivated malicious activity tracked by Unit 42. The actors behind this intrusion set have used 01flip ransomware and Sliver implants in attacks against organizations in the Asia-Pacific region, including critical infrastructure. The group is associated with manual exploitation, data leaks on dark web forums, and ransomware deployment.",
